<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
  <head>
    <%- include('./common/_head', {title: "B-1"}); %>
  </head>

  <body class="sidebar-rectangle">
    <div id="wrapper">
      <div class="bg-video">
        <video autoplay muted loop>
          <source src="./images/video.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
        </video>
      </div>

      <header id="header-navbar">
        <nav class="d-flex flex-column">
          <a class="header-logo" href="/"
            ><img
              src="./images/logo-header@2x.png"
              alt="Stake Technologies, Inc."
          /></a>
          <div class="header-nav">
            <a href="#">Service</a>
            <a href="#">Media</a>
            <a href="#">Company</a>
            <a href="#">Career</a>
            <a href="#">Contact</a>
          </div>
          <a href="#" class="language"
            ><i class="material-icons">language</i><span>日本語</span></a
          >
        </nav>
      </header>

      <div id="hero">
        <div class="hero-content d-flex align-items-center">
          <div class="container">
            <div class="hero-content-inner">
              <h1 class="mb-3 hero-title">Web3.0を実現する</h1>
              <p class="mb-5 hero-text">
                Stake
                Technologiesはブロックチェーンなどの最先端技術を用い次世代の分散型WebであるWeb3.0、そしてその先に社会の再分散化を目指すテクノロジー企業です。
              </p>
              <div class="d-flex hero-buttons">
                <a href="#" class="btn btn-outline-primary btn-lg">Service</a>
                <a href="#" class="btn btn-outline-primary btn-lg"
                  >Who We Are</a
                >
                <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Contact</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div id="who-we-are" class="text-center">
        <img src="./images/who-we-are@2x.png" alt="" />
      </div>

      <div id="service">
        <img src="./images/service@2x.png" alt="" />
      </div>

      <div id="media">
        <img src="./images/media@2x.png" alt="" />
      </div>
    </div>

    <script>
      $(function () {
        var navPos = jQuery("#header-navbar").offset().top;
        var navHeight = $(window).height();
        jQuery(window).on("scroll", function () {
          if (jQuery(this).scrollTop() > navHeight) {
            jQuery("#header-navbar").addClass("fixed");
          } else {
            jQuery("#header-navbar").removeClass("fixed");
          }
        });
      });
    </script>
  </body>
</html>
